1
00:00:00,725 --> 00:00:03,580
It's true, then, what they're saying on
the train.

2
00:00:04,624 --> 00:00:06,460
Harry Potter has come to Hogwarts.

3
00:00:07,080 --> 00:00:08,100
Harry Potter.

4
00:00:09,240 --> 00:00:11,380
This is Crabbe and Goyle.

5
00:00:12,345 --> 00:00:13,345
And I'm Malfoy.

6
00:00:14,915 --> 00:00:16,200
Draco Malfoy.

7
00:00:19,080 --> 00:00:20,380
Think my name is funny, do you?

8
00:00:20,890 --> 00:00:22,140
With no need to ask you yours.

9
00:00:22,920 --> 00:00:25,460
Red hair and a hand-me-down robe.

10
00:00:26,300 --> 00:00:27,440
You must be a Weasley.

11
00:00:29,800 --> 00:00:33,780
You'll soon find out that some wizarding
families are better than others, Potter.

12
00:00:33,999 --> 00:00:36,260
You don't want to go making friends with
the wrong sort.

13
00:00:37,889 --> 00:00:38,889
I can help you there.

14
00:00:42,100 --> 00:00:44,580
I think I can tell the wrong sort for
myself, thanks.

